							"imageAltTextGen3":"\"Chess World Championship 2021 3D model for Blender 3D software - photorealistic chess set used in the FIDE world chess championship 2021 between Carlsen and Nepomnjaschtschi. This high-quality model accurately replicates the tournament's chess board and pieces, perfect for game development and visualization projects. Download and enjoy the realistic rendering in Octane render with sun glare and warm sunlight effects.\"",
